125},"ISic001694","Fragment of a public inscription",{"_":12},{"title":2,"author":3,"date":4,"citation":5,"uri":6,"ref":119},{"_":125,"ana":126,"ref":127},{"_":19,"ana":20,"ref":21},{"_":23,"ana":24,"ref":25},{"ana":132},{"layout":309},{"p":310,"rs":311,"damage":312},"Remains of two columns of text, with a space between of 1-2.5 cm. The right margin of the left column (A) is uneven, with a vacat equivalent to two line ends above the end of the first visibile line of text; the left margin of the right column is consistent.",{"_":30,"ana":31,"ref":32},{"ana":313},"#text_condition.incomplete",{"lettering":315,"dimensions":316},"Arena notes that the quadrangular module of the individual letters is somewhat irregular, with the combined module of omicron-nu (used as a control across multiple similar fragments) being 10mm from centre to centre. Letters with neat terminal serifs, elegantly cut.",[317,320],{"type":36,"l":318,"from":38,"to":319,"h":253,"unit":39,"atLeast":253,"atMost":253},"Line 1-5","line5",{"type":41,"l":255,"from":38,"to":319,"h":256,"unit":39,"atLeast":256,"atMost":256},{"_":322,"notBefore":259,"notAfter":323,"evidence":261},"Later 2nd century BCE or early C1 BCE",-51,[325,326],{"_":50,"type":51,"ref":52},{"_":54,"type":55,"ref":56,"offset":57},[328],[60,61],[],{"_":271,"role":272,"ref":273},{"_":332,"type":276},"ME30906",{"_":72,"mainLang":73,"languages":334},[72],[336,337],{"atLeast":283,"atMost":283},{"atLeast":285,"atMost":285},[92],[102],[341,342,343,125,19,23,108,109,110,111,112,294,114,73],"isic001694","fragment of a public inscription",{"_":12},"\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Cspan class=\"textpartnumber\" style=\"left: -4em;\">Col. 1\u003Cbr>\u003C/span>  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">(vac.3)\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\"